candidates.body:
Chore:

- Ensure compatibility with preserve_order feature of schemars #78

candidates.title: Ensure compatibility with preserve_order feature of schemars
candidates.body: When using the `preserve_order` feature of `schemars`, `BTreeMap` is internally replaced with an `IndexMap`, which does not have the `first_key_value()` method. This PR uses `iter().next()`, which has the same semantics, but is available both in `BTreeMap` and `IndexMap`.
